						<li><b>Total Amount Due : </b>The sum of all the items listed on the invoice, including any
							applicable taxes and discounts.</li>
						<li><b>Payment Terms : </b>Information about when the payment is due, such as "Net 30" (payment
							is due within 30 days of the invoice date).</li>
						<li><b>Terms and Conditions : </b>Any specific terms or conditions related to the sale, such as
							return policies or late payment penalties.</li>
